title: My account name on Boards says "MY ACCOUNT", match history gives 401 error?
body:
Help...?
Attempting to vote on threads gives me the Amumu face error?

replies.body: How did you upload the photos ?
Clear your Browser History just as Targons Blade says.

Does this happen if you log into your board profile using a different browser or after clearing your browser's cache using [this guide](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752694-Clearing-Browser-History-and-Cookies)?

Thank you very much!

I had the same problem as OP and clearing Browser History did fix the problem.

If OP hadn't run into the same problem I would still be stuck not being about to be a part of the boards.

Thank you again!
